{% extends "page.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="sub">
            This Privacy Policy explains what information Clean Gutters Crew collects, how it is used, and your choices.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <p>Last updated: February 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you request a quote or contact us, we may collect:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>City and postal code</li>
            <li>Street address</li>
            <li>Service details and notes</li>
            <li>Photos you choose to upload (optional)</li>
            <li>Preferred contact method</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We only collect information that is reasonably necessary to respond to your request and provide our services.</p>

        <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Respond to quote requests</li>
            <li>Contact you about your request</li>
            <li>Schedule appointments</li>
            <li>Provide pricing and service details</li>
            <li>Improve our service quality and operations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>

        <h2>3. How your information is stored</h2>
        <p>Your information may be stored in our business email and in tools we use to manage requests and scheduling. We take reasonable safeguards to protect information from loss, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.</p>

        <h2>4. Sharing of information</h2>
        <p>We may share your information only when necessary:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>With team members or contractors performing the requested service</li>
            <li>With service providers that help operate our website or communication tools</li>
            <li>When required by law</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell or rent personal information to third parties.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies, analytics, and anti-spam tools</h2>
        <p>Our website may use basic cookies or similar technologies to maintain site functionality, improve performance, and protect against abuse. If we use Google reCAPTCHA, Google may collect technical information according to Google’s policies.</p>

        <h2>6. Your consent</h2>
        <p>By submitting information through our website or contacting us, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this policy. You may withdraw consent at any time by contacting us, subject to legal or contractual restrictions.</p>

        <h2>7. Your rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access to your personal information, ask us to correct inaccurate information, or request deletion where appropriate. We may need to verify your identity before responding.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or requests about this Privacy Policy, contact:</p>
        <p>
            Clean Gutters Crew<br>
            Email: <a href="mailto:cgc.services.bc@gmail.com">cgc.services.bc@gmail.com</a><br>
            Phone: <a href="tel:+16725006060">+1 (672) 500-6060</a><br>
            Service area: Metro Vancouver, BC, Canada
        </p>

        <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The “Last updated” date at the top will reflect the latest version.</p>
    </div>



{% endblock %}